egory>scholarship</category><category>Section 25A</category><category>Tax Stimulus Package</category><category>The American Opportunity Tax Credit. But</category><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">info@1031podcast.com (Jeffery R. Peterson)</dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2009 09:00:55 PDT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.1031podcast.com/?p=141</guid><content:encoded xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><![CDATA[<div class="media">
