its</category><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">info@1031podcast.com (Jeffery R. Peterson)</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2009 01:54:59 PDT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.1031podcast.com/?p=135</guid><content:encoded xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><![CDATA[<div class="media">
